    <p>
        This <a target="_blank" href="https://www.syncfusion.com/aspnet-core-ui-controls/charts/chart-types/area-chart">ASP.NET Core Area Chart</a> example visualizes music sales data by format in US by using a default area series in the chart.
    </p>
}
